snippet.textDisplay:
A question for the indian fans:

Imagine in WT20 2020, if at a crucial point in a knockout match, if Kohli or Sharma are dismissed in the same manner and ind ends up losing, what would ur reaction be?
B4 anybody starts swearing, it's an honest Q, jus wana know ur opinion.
Personally, i agree with it. A bowler is not even allowed to step over the line n if he does... No ball n free hit given.

The sport's laws are already in the favour of the batsmen.

I was all for Senanayeke doing it to Buttler. And what amazes me is how Buttler called Matthews a "cheating f**k" in that same match afterwards. Im glad he got the same treatment in ipl.
